GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?page=1&pageSize=5

###

### Test 3: Pagination - Second page
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?page=2&pageSize=2

###

### Test 4: Search by first name
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?search=john

###

### Test 5: Search by email
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?search=example.com

