### Test 6: Filter active users only
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?isActive=true

###

### Test 7: Sort by first name ascending
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?sortBy=firstName&sortOrder=asc

###

### Test 8: Sort by email descending
GET http://localhost:5099/api/users?sortBy=email&sortOrder=desc

###

